npm2spec
========

This project aims at providing an easy way to generate a spec file
for projects hosted on npm:
http://npmjs.org

Important!  It can recursively extract and try to package dependencies.
Try it like so:

    $ npm2spec --verbose --recurse SOME_NPM_PACKAGE

Dependencies:
------------
- python-rdflib >= 3.0.0
- python-argparse
- python-jinja2
- python-sh
